config BR2_PACKAGE_LED_SERVER
	bool "led-server"
	help
	  UDP server that receives LED pattern commands from a PC and writes
	  them to the FPGA LED PIO register on the DE10-Nano.

	  Phase 7 Track A — HPS Ethernet LED control.

	  Protocol (2-byte request / 2-byte response):
	    CMD 0x01 = SET_PATTERN
	    CMD 0x02 = GET_PATTERN

	  https://github.com/bleviet/cvsoc
